{"tid":348742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"\"奶\"匙羹放糖罐 變成命案 ，茶客改被控誤殺","createTime":"2017-08-06T03:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T02:28:10.000Z","uid":24824,"like":335,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e08e7c17c94e0c385f168a56b9bf8eb9c1908627","tid":348742,"uid":24824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T03:39:38.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=85LsdYHTUHxkbjS562haYY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=37f7c853\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 58歲「奶茶叔」黃文權去年10月10日在茶餐廳為奶茶加糖時，因將私羹「舔完」試味後再插落公用糖罐，引起同枱食客不滿而演變毆鬥，最終「奶茶叔」受傷命危，46歲食客梁寶鈿被控一項傷人罪，案件原於今日在觀塘法院再訊。惟由於黃文權延至上周六(16日)不治，警方遂將控罪改為誤殺。 <br />\n<br />\n控方今日在庭上申請將案件押後至3月22日，等待死者的醫生及驗屍報告後再訊，獲裁判官批准，而被告繼續獲准保釋。 <br />\n<br />\n修訂控罪指，梁寶鈿在去年10月10日在觀塘順天邨天權樓的萬順茶餐廳外，非法殺死58歲男子黃文權。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160119/photo/bkn-20160119102748758-0119_00822_001_01p.jpg?20160119112258\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160119%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160119102748758-0119_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20160119112258&h=6d1e089a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae6fccadae042a6a48921989378171a86e1d723e","tid":348742,"uid":11417,"like":571,"dislike":1,"score":570,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T03:40:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a532df5b1908662a48f3190cbcc8edc3d720c42e","tid":348742,"uid":19552,"like":360,"dislike":2,"score":358,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T03:41:01.000Z","msg":"明明條廢老仆街 又係佢聊人打"},{"pid":"e5094a818461ea4299dcde5e5513c25858799a12","tid":348742,"uid":24824,"like":224,"dislike":0,"score":224,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T03:41:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明廢老抵死</blockquote><br />\n梁生好撚慘"},{"pid":"17a12dc8270c1e46ffac95f4eb949c14